description: Contains the works of Adam de la Halle from f. 1-68, including the 16 polyphonic Rondeaux and 5 motets, together with many other pieces in verse, such as Richart de Fournival's 'Bestiaire' and Jacquemars Gelée of Lille's 'Renart le Nouvel'.
